content:
Looking at search parameters that point to different extensions in the plan net profiles I noticed that they point to different (vhdir) extensions than the ones called out in the resources themselves
for instance this search parameter https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/davinci-pdex-plan-net/SearchParameter-organization-coverage-area.html uses http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/StructureDefinition/location-reference while the Network profile seems to use http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pdex-plan-net/StructureDefinition/location-reference
is this just uncorrected from a move away from vhdir? or am I missing something here?
Good catch. Organization::coverage-plan is the only vhdir vestige I found. If I can fix at this point, I will.
